upload.js is a file uploader webapp Ã  la gmail file attachment uploader.

The following dependencies are mandatory (use 'npm install <dependency>', use npm 1.0.17 or better and run from the project root):
- formidable
- nodeunit
- zombie

Runs successfully on node 0.4.10

To execute the tests, execute: 
	nodeunit spec/*.js
	
The tests cover the storage (file system)

To run the web server, execute:
	node controller/index.js

Then hit http://localhost:8099